Here's the updated `schema.prisma` file with the new `User` model:

```
datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

model User {
  id        Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  email     String   @unique
  fullName  String
  password  String
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @default(now())
}
```

Please note that you will also need to run the `prisma migrate dev` command to apply the changes to your database schema.